Summary: In his hands, deck of playing cards is more dangerous than the gun, but to win a poker tournament is not only necessary to be able to play ... Among his rivals stands Annabelle Bransford (Jodie Foster) who while Brett former admires her, she was trying to rob him. Along the way the race everyone is keen to play the other and it is difficult to say who will take home the grand prize ...
